  "description": "<p><strong>英特尔CEO科再奇(Brian Krzanich)预计，英特尔芯片将于2013年底之前被应用于可穿戴计算设备。科再奇本人已试用谷歌眼镜一段时间。</strong>与前任保罗·欧德宁(Paul Otellini)不同，科再奇对英特尔的网络电视业务持谨慎态度。他表示：“我们是硅的专家，是移动技术的专家，推动了摩尔定律的发展。但我们并不是内 容行业专家，因此我们需要谨慎。”英特尔对网络电视业务有很高的期望，而早期评测者也给出了不错的评价，不过英特尔尚未与任何一家内容提供商达成合作协 议。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e0bd102/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243073.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E5%B0%94%E5%8F%AF%E7%A9%BF%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243073.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E5%B0%94%E5%8F%AF%E7%A9%BF%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243073.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E5%B0%94%E5%8F%AF%E7%A9%BF%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243073.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E5%B0%94%E5%8F%AF%E7%A9%BF%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbe